Considere nivel de confianca de 95% e teste bicaudal para os testes abaixo.

Status Quo

sq <- 30

# amostra
set.seed(764939)
a <- rnorm(30, 30, 20)

teste.t(a, mu=sq)

## 
##  One Sample t-test
## 
## data:  x
## t = -0.63228, df = 29, p-value = 0.5322
## alternative hypothesis: true mean is not equal to 30
## 95 percent confidence interval:
##  20.62788 34.94578
## sample estimates:
## mean of x 
##  27.78683

Grupos Pareados

set.seed(764939)
x <- rnorm(10,2.35,1.80)
y <- rnorm(10,3.93,2.40)


teste.t(x, y, paired = TRUE, var.equal = TRUE)

## 
##  Paired t-test
## 
## data:  x and y
## t = -2.216, df = 9, p-value = 0.05391
## alternative hypothesis: true difference in means is not equal to 0
## 95 percent confidence interval:
##  -4.09079156  0.04214098
## sample estimates:
## mean of the differences 
##               -2.024325

Grupos Independentes - variancias iguais

set.seed(57840)
a1 <- rnorm(25, 21.989, 1.1535)

set.seed(57840)
a2 <- rnorm(30, 20.91, 1.3465)


# x menor que y eh o mesmo que ...
# Aqui Ã© a1 < a2
teste.t(a1, a2, var.equal = TRUE, alternative="less")

## 
##  Two Sample t-test
## 
## data:  x and y
## t = 2.6903, df = 53, p-value = 0.9952
## alternative hypothesis: true difference in means is less than 0
## 95 percent confidence interval:
##      -Inf 1.921393
## sample estimates:
## mean of x mean of y 
##  22.19480  21.01043
# y maior que x.
# Ã o mesmo que a2 > a1
teste.t(a2, a1, var.equal = TRUE, alternative="greater")

## 
##  Two Sample t-test
## 
## data:  x and y
## t = -2.6903, df = 53, p-value = 0.9952
## alternative hypothesis: true difference in means is greater than 0
## 95 percent confidence interval:
##  -1.921393       Inf
## sample estimates:
## mean of x mean of y 
##  21.01043  22.19480

Grupos Independentes - variancias diferentes

set.seed(578501)
a1 <- rnorm(23, 21.98, 1.168)

set.seed(57840)
a2 <- rnorm(32, 21.2627, 2.43025)



# x menor que y eh o mesmo que ...
# Aqui Ã© a1 < a2
teste.t(a1, a2, var.equal = FALSE, alternative="less")

# y maior que x.
# Ã o mesmo que a2 > a1
teste.t(a2, a1, var.equal = FALSE, alternative="greater")
